se except for the purpose described in Section 1. Party One and Party Two each agrees not to disclose the confidential information to others, without the express written permission of the other party.\n\n5. Future Development.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3817, "end_char_idx": 4163, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "0fd43bb4-4f1e-429a-8013-7c1d1d32491e": {"__data__": {"id_": "0fd43bb4-4f1e-429a-8013-7c1d1d32491e", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "ce11175b-8092-41a4-9e0f-279eac67f3b0", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bce7064881f9882a6885902a8afccb393631a37b57c19fe201e4fe822c2f14bc", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "a6734730-52a2-4872-88f1-0b15bf0e6ae0", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "cc923a4cb44391821b932a52eae8fbf981f1a389078b8d57cca1086617c8e71e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "5d181f53-286c-4874-bd40-1e120b0fb12b", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f905573feba1b8fe3ca19575feffb48f5332c0234515765783c1e6c4149fb1d4", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Party Two shall not directly or indirectly acquire any interest in,\n\n or design, create, manufacture, sell or otherwise deal with any item or product, based upon or derived from the Confidential Information provided by Party One , except as may be expressly agreed to in writing by Party One .\n\n6. Property  Rights,  Return  of  Materials .", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4164, "end_char_idx": 4504, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "5d181f53-286c-4874-bd40-1e120b0fb12b": {"__data__": {"id_": "5d181f53-286c-4874-bd40-1e120b0fb12b", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}