ement  from  any  person  obtaining  access  to  the  Confidential  Information  pursuant  to  this paragraph 7, and shall advise the other party in writing of the manner of such disclosure.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 5382, "end_char_idx": 5732, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "124f28a0-045d-4a83-bafe-48832efe14a6": {"__data__": {"id_": "124f28a0-045d-4a83-bafe-48832efe14a6", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "ce11175b-8092-41a4-9e0f-279eac67f3b0", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bce7064881f9882a6885902a8afccb393631a37b57c19fe201e4fe822c2f14bc", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "8c5e86a4-2563-42d0-a62d-648dc3ec1f32", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "390c580649c87d0045ec1105de6154187b60f3c40b28f231ccda0d9fdca193c3", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "01f86816-2f84-49e3-a377-95c6809a5c86", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "7c61814d5157025a70e85379174964a25ab79d5fd8e9c85e1add9089a3821376", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Confidential Document\nDesign 1st Inc.1\n\nMUTUAL NON-DISCLOSURE AGREEMENT\n\n8. Information  Not  Confidential.\n\n Information  shall  be  deemed  not  to  be  confidential  if  such  information  is  or  becomes publicly known through no wrongful act of the receiving party, or is already known by the receiving party as evidenced by competent  proof  thereof,", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 5734, "end_char_idx": 6090, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "01f86816-2f84-49e3-a377-95c6809a5c86": {"__data__": {"id_": "01f86816-2f84-49e3-a377-95c6809a5c86", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "ce11175b-8092-41a4-9e0f-279eac67f3b0", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bce7064881f9882a6885902a8afccb393631a37b57c19fe201e4fe822c2f14bc", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "124f28a0-045d-4a83-bafe-48832efe14a6", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "2d9c392bbf4cc9f1e0bd5ce51915359135069dc1daa8d0ddc07b75152c4cf949", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "30412287-3321-4295-80e2-b282089748d4", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a4c74e2aa0cf92e6e66afb27478b169905ec88e18defb93333f5394cc12df7a4", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "or  is  approved  for  release  by  the  prior  written  approval  of  the  disclosing  party,  or  is  rightfully received by the receiving party from a third party without restriction and without breach of this agreement, or is disclosed by the  disclosing  party  to  a  third  party  without  a  similar  restriction  on  the  rights  of  such  third  party,", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 6092, "end_char_idx": 6454, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "30412287-3321-4295-80e2-b282089748d4": {"__data__": {"id_": "30412287-3321-4295-80e2-b282089748d4", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "ce11175b-8092-41a4-9e0f-279eac67f3b0", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bce7064881f9882a6885902a8afccb393631a37b57c19fe201e4fe822c2f14bc", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "01f86816-2f84-49e3-a377-95c6809a5c86", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "7c61814d5157025a70e85379174964a25ab79d5fd8e9c85e1add9089a3821376", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "683b07d8-ba01-47a1-ab3c-fa5ccbd20c4f", "node_